WikiTrust is a project to compute text reputation for all
articles in the Wikipedia.  WikiTrust-FF is a Firefox plugin
which modifies the Wikipedia website to add a "WikiTrust"
tab to view a colored version of the article. 

The Firefox plugin is available for download at
   https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/11087/

The main WikiTrust project page is at
   http://www.wikitrust.net/

